ght sets. Louis Gordon is partnering Adam Player in the doubles and they played a great match to win in the first round and they now play no 2 seeds Ben Matthews and Kieran Booth tomorrow afternoon. Good luck\r\n\r\nA big congratulations to both Charlie and Adam on reaching their first British Open main draw and great experience for them both!\r\n\r\n<strong>Courts this week and weekend</strong>\r\nFriday 20th November\r\nCourt available to book at 07.45 and 20.15\r\n\r\nSaturday 21st November\r\nCourt available to book at 07.45, 16.30, 19.00 and 20.15\r\n\r\nSunday 22nd November\r\nCourts available to book at 09.00, 19.00 and 20.15 – Louis available for a lesson at 09.00\r\n\r\nIf any of these courts suit you then do book online at <a href=\"http://www.realtennisonline.com/bookings\">www.realtennisonline.com/bookings</a> or call myself or Louis at the club on 01798 343527.','Week of 16th November - News/results at PHTC','','inherit','closed','closed','','44-revision-v1','','','2015-11-20 13:50:59','2015-11-20 13:50:59','',44,'http://phtcdev.jonpetersen.co.uk/2015/11/20/44-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(61,1,'2015-11-20 13:56:38','2015-11-20 13:56:38','<table width=\"615\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\">\r\n                          <col width=\"64\" span=\"2\" />\r\n                          <col width=\"128\" span=\"2\" />\r\n                          <col width=\"201\" />\r\n                          <tr height=\"19\">\r\n                            <td width=\"128\" height=\"19\" colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"><strong>&nbsp;Handicap\r\n                              Difference</strong></td>\r\n                            <td width=\"128\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"><strong>Receiving Player</strong></td>\r\n                            <td width=\"128\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"><strong>Owing Player</strong></td>\r\n                            <td width=\"201\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"><strong>Additional Handicap</strong></td>\r\n                      