/pdf',0),(258,1,'2015-11-24 18:03:25','2015-11-24 18:03:25','<a href=\"http://phtcdev.jonpetersen.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/PHTC-2015-V1.pdf\">View From The Grille - April 2015 (PDF)</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://phtcdev.jonpetersen.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/PHTC-2014.pdf\">View From The Grille - November 2014 (PDF)</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://phtcdev.jonpetersen.co.uk/email-newsletter-november-2014/\">Email Newsletter November 2014</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://phtcdev.jonpetersen.co.uk/newsletters/email-news-november-2013/\">Email Newsletter November 2013</a>','Newsletters','','inherit','closed','closed','','240-revision-v1','','','2015-11-24 18:03:25','2015-11-24 18:03:25','',240,'http://phtcdev.jonpetersen.co.uk/2015/11/24/240-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(259,1,'2015-11-25 14:19:43','2015-11-25 14:19:43','','Chase One Real Tennis Marker','','publish','closed','closed','','chase-one-real-tennis-marker','','','2015-12-08 23:05:05','2015-12-08 23:05:05','',0,'http://phtcdev.jonpetersen.co.uk/?p=259',11,'nav_menu_item','',0),(262,1,'2015-11-25 14:31:47','2015-11-25 14:31:47','','TheLawsOfTennis','','inherit','open','closed','','thelawsoftennis-3','','','2015-11-25 14:31:47','2015-11-25 14:31:47','',0,'http://phtcdev.jonpetersen.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/TheLawsOfTennis2.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pdf',0),(265,1,'2015-11-25 14:51:12','2015-11-25 14:51:12','<strong>Senior Professional, Petworth House Tennis Court.</strong>\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><a href=\"http://phtcdev.jonpetersen.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Durack3_lrg.jpg\"><img class=\"none alignleft wp-image-183 size-full\" src=\"http://phtcdev.jonpetersen.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Durack3_lrg.jpg\" alt=\"Durack3_lrg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" data-id=\"183\" /></a></strong> \r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>Status</strong>: Professional\r\n<strong>World Ranking</strong>: Top 50\r\n<strong>Nationality</strong>: British\r\n<strong>Ranking Points</strong>: 209\r\n<strong>Handicap</strong>: 5\r\n<strong>Left/Right Handed</strong>: Right\r\n<strong>D.O.B.</strong>: 13/05/1982\r\n<strong>Basic Certificate Passed</strong>: 2001\r\n<strong>Hobbies</strong>: Snowboarding, Travel, Cars</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nTom came from a lawn tennis background and joined Chris Bray at Petworth in 2000 as a trainee. Under Chris’s tutelage Tom’s tennis has thrived and continues to do so. With the departure of Chris Bray from Petworth in 2005, Tom’s tennis continued to improve under Petworth’s new Head Professional Nick Wood.\r\n\r\nIn 2007 Chris Bray returned to the club and in 2011 Chris and Tom both took on a new challenge working on a part time basis at the Holyport Real tennis Club to revive the fortunes of the club. Tom assisted Chris for 3 years and they managed to increase the playing membership from 45-185 whilst still working at the Petworth Club. A fantastic achievement.\r\n\r\nIn 2015 Tom hopes to turn his attention back to competitive play and is partnering the world number 4 Bryn Sayers in the Premier Division of the National League. Tom is also heavily involved in the thriving Junior sector at Petworth and is highly regard for his teaching of youth tennis.\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>\r\n				<strong>Tournament</strong>\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th>\r\n				<strong>Round</strong>\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th>\r\n				<strong>Opponent</strong>\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th>\r\n				<strong>Result</strong>\r\n			</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				British Open Singles 2015\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Last 16\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Steve Virgona\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				6/1 6/0 6/1\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				British Open Singles 2013\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Last 32\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Andrew Lyons\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				6/1 6/1 5/6 6/4\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				The Inaugural MURTC British Challenge\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>